Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's like a tornado and a battalion came through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far worse than what was reported to headquarters. We'd better quicken our pace and find Lieutenant Havoc
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter Al you forget how to walk in a straight line? Stop bumping into me. Sorry these
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoky places give me the creeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you got the heebie-jeebies Al you're a suit of armor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the lieutenant walking all bravely up there leading the way and she's just a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to insult you in any way. I swear. I just meant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We surrounded why can't they make all this noise when they're hiding no choice boys get ready for a fight
